})

    game.splash("GAME OVER")

            blockSettings.clear()
            level = 0

        call_level(level, level)
    } else if (option == "HeadBob") {
        blockMenu.showMenu(["Off", "On"], MenuStyle.List, MenuLocation.BottomHalf)
        blockMenu.setSelectedIndex(0)
    } else if (option == "Off" || option == "On") {
        bob = blockMenu.selectedMenuIndex()
        menu2()
    }
})
